{\pard\b\fs30 1. Introduction\par}
The FIDA Android app is a gamified fitness application designed to promote daily physical activity through real-time tracking, streaks, badges, and rewards. The app integrates GPS-based run tracking, step counting, water intake logging, sleep monitoring, and a comprehensive reward economy. Testing objectives include validating functional correctness, ensuring data consistency, and UI responsiveness.\par
